Show HN: Comics Written and Drawn by AI
text:
Hey, I made a website which outputs daily comics written and drawn by a machine. https://dailyaicomics.com

I know it's fun to ask ChatGPT for a joke about X, but I wanted to take a step further by asking it for:

1. a comic in three parts 2. to include lines and a title 3. prompts to draw it

I'm asking ChatGPT to output JSON with the comic and then I parse it and move it to the next step of the pipeline (drawing). Tools on their own are cool, but chaining them is the true multiplier of creativity.

Check the source on Github: https://github.com/infomiho/dailyaicomics

The hardest thing so far was figuring out how to get a bit more consistent style since each panel is draw in isolation. I've tried asking "draw in the style of X famous comic writer" but that had two drawbacks: - their style varies (color, black and white) - since it's a comic author, it oftentimes draws a whole comic (multiple panels)

Now I'm being very explicit around the style (ink, pastel colors etc.) and it's okay.

I'm wondering what's the best approach to get consistency?

SaaS for Realtime/AI data cleaning and summarizing (Need feedback)
text:
Hello all, Applying for YC S23, how does the 1 liner sound. Here is more on the same. Let me know if the above helps justify what it is doing.

Problem: unclean data goes without any intervention for a long time. So it will take space & also no value is generated. Our solution: will act as a crawler/filter to store only what has value Definition of value: it is like what is statistically significant

So what I am building is a SaaS that will do all the preparation before an analyst starts his work. Just like a chef gets his veggies chopped before he starts. So an analyst has to do 3 steps primarily 1. Gather data 2. Clean data 3. Do the exploratory or initial statistical analysis My SaaS helps in steps 2 & 3. Also it will generate an information score to show the value of the data. Also btw this is completely automated with no interaction needed.

I have the following ones in mind 1. Preliminary analysis of your data 2. Auto clean & summaries of your data. 3. Give Pre analyzed and cleaned data 4. All is meant to do in real time

Incase you know any competitors/ you find no value please do let me know.
